title: RARE Disney Movie - Secret Of Boyne Castle (1969)
description: This is the 1969 Disney Miniseries, all 3 parts are present and accounted for, starring Kurt Russell in a spy drama that mainly spans between England and Ireland. Boy becomes unknowingly caught in the middle, when a message is delivered for his brother through him, from a dying man shot by the KGB. The KGB wants that message and will stop at nothing to get it. Based on the Book Guns In The Heather. Shown as part of The Wonderful World Of Disney under the title Secret Of Boyne Castle, released theatricaly in England ( a shortened version) as Guns In The Heather and resurfacing on the Disney channle in early 80s with yet another title "Spybusters" very good, very rare film
